{"tid":346081,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"鷹 眼 再 重 申 現 時 單 身","createTime":"2017-08-03T15:34:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-04T00:50:41.000Z","uid":35964,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"34ff3b8c91c8d8eafc2b6fda0cc0b88d79e4e931","tid":346081,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T15:34:25.000Z","msg":"繼《復仇者聯盟》後，「鷹眼」謝洛美溫納（Jeremy Renner）和「紅女巫」伊莉莎伯奧遜（Elizabeth Olsen）再度合演新片《風河谷謀殺案》（Wind River），昨晚在紐約舉行試映會，二人盛裝亮相，穿著Christian Dior灰色連身長裙的伊莉莎伯更是明艷照人。<br />\n<br />\n為了宣傳新片，謝洛美早前接受《Men's Journal》雜誌訪問，自爆憧憬家裏有8名子女在跑跑跳跳的熱鬧生活，說罷卻又自嘲目前仍是獨身，「此時此刻，我暫時看不見將來會出現這個畫面」，未知謝婷婷聽罷有何感想？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170803/s00007/8dd62057ea0d2b4b18bb60844b2e4a23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170803%2Fs00007%2F8dd62057ea0d2b4b18bb60844b2e4a23.jpg&h=515bf470&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"253834eba0e2e06b33c2dfb5f9a72218114981a3","tid":346081,"uid":24641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T15:41:17.000Z","msg":"Elizabeth Olsen真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0446d54eb45980e453b1e694f7411b220d263f","tid":346081,"uid":105715,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T15:46:15.000Z","msg":"可能含過幾次撚就以為自己係女友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944db6671ea4d27b5389a12366c03fa49e5e6563","tid":346081,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T15:52:42.000Z","msg":"鷹眼個樣做乜老左咁多"},{"pid":"71caaf6104178570c7f6740cee82b5fc0ca9b067","tid":346081,"uid":14497,"like":0,"dislik